## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data and the rapidly evolving nature of the COVID-19 pandemic. The situation regarding global freedoms is dynamic, and new developments may alter the current understanding. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources means that the findings are contingent on the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the original reports. Further research and primary data collection would be beneficial to corroborate these findings.

